  "body": "\n\n<div class=\"orh-outer\">\n<div class=\"orh-grid\"></div>\n<div class=\"orh-glow\"></div>\n<div class=\"orh-inner\">\n<div class=\"orh-label orh-rev\"><div class=\"orh-label-dot\"></div>Free Construction Resources</div>\n<h1 class=\"orh-h1 orh-rev orh-d1\">Learn. Compare.<br/><span class=\"orh-h1-em\">Build Smarter.</span></h1>\n<p class=\"orh-sub orh-rev orh-d2\">Case studies from real SiteFlow clients, expert guides on construction management, software comparisons and free IS-code calculators — built for Indian contractors.</p>\n<div class=\"orh-pills orh-rev orh-d3\">\n Case Studies — COLOR: icon bg/stroke rose \n<a class=\"orh-pill\" href=\"#res-case-studies\">\n<div class=\"orh-pill-icon\" style=\"background:#fff0f3!important;\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"16\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M9 11l3 3L22 4\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg></div>\n<div class=\"orh-pill-text\"><span class=\"orh-pill-name\">Case Studies</span><span class=\"orh-pill-count\">Real client results</span></div>\n</a>\n Blog Articles — green kept \n<a class=\"orh-pill\" href=\"#res-blog\">\n<div class=\"orh-pill-icon\" style=\"background:#d1fae5!important;\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"16\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h10\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg></div>\n<div class=\"orh-pill-text\"><span class=\"orh-pill-name\">Blog Articles</span><span class=\"orh-pill-count\">Guides and how-tos</span></div>\n</a>\n Comparisons — amber kept \n<a class=\"orh-pill\" href=\"#res-comparisons\">\n<div class=\"orh-pill-icon\" style=\"background:#fef3c7!important;\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"16\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M18 20V10M12 20V4M6 20v-6\" stroke=\"#b45309\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg></div>\n<div class=\"orh-pill-text\"><span class=\"orh-pill-name\">Comparisons</span><span class=\"orh-pill-count\">SiteFlow vs alternatives</span></div>\n</a>\n Free Calculators — blue kept \n<a class=\"orh-pill\" href=\"#res-calculators\">\n<div class=\"orh-pill-icon\" style=\"background:#dbeafe!important;\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"16\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"16\"><rect height=\"20\" rx=\"2\" stroke=\"#1d4ed8\" stroke-width=\"2\" width=\"16\" x=\"4\" y=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M8 6h8M8 10h8M8 14h4\" stroke=\"#1d4ed8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg></div>\n<div class=\"orh-pill-text\"><span class=\"orh-pill-name\">Free Calculators</span><span class=\"orh-pill-count\">IS code based tools</span></div>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<span id=\"res-calculators\" style=\"display:block!important;height:0!important;\"></span>\n<div class=\"orcc-outer\">\n<div class=\"orcc-inner\">\n<div class=\"orcc-head orcc-rev\">\n<div class=\"orcc-head-l\"><div class=\"orcc-ey\">Free Tools</div><h2 class=\"orcc-h2\">Construction <em class=\"orcc-h2-em\">Calculators</em></h2></div>\n<a class=\"orcc-va\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/construction-calculators/\">View all calculators<svg class=\"orcc-va-arrow\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"orcc-grid\">\n 1. Steel — Column — COLOR: icon stroke rose \n<a class=\"orcc-card orcc-rev orcc-d1\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/steel-calculator-for-construction/\">\n<div class=\"orcc-icon orcc-ic-purple\"><svg class=\"orcc-icon-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect height=\"20\" rx=\"2\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" width=\"8\" x=\"8\" y=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 7h16M4 17h16\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path><path d=\"M12 2v20\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-dasharray=\"2 2\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"></path></svg></div>\n<div class=\"orcc-badge\">Free Tool</div>\n<h3 class=\"orcc-title\">Steel Calculator for Column</h3>\n<p class=\"orcc-desc\">Main bars, stirrups, lap length and total steel weight for RCC columns. IS 456:2000 formula — D² ÷ 163.</p>\n<div class=\"orcc-chips\"><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Main bar kg</span><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Stirrup kg</span><span class=\"orcc-chip-g\">Total weight</span><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Est. cost</span></div>\n<span class=\"orcc-btn\">Use Calculator<span class=\"orcc-ai\">AI</span><svg class=\"orcc-btn-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span>\n</a>\n 2. Steel — One-Way Slab \n<a class=\"orcc-card orcc-rev orcc-d2\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/steel-calculator-for-construction/\">\n<div class=\"orcc-icon orcc-ic-purple\"><svg class=\"orcc-icon-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect height=\"10\" rx=\"2\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" width=\"20\" x=\"2\" y=\"7\"></rect><path d=\"M6 7v10M10 7v10M14 7v10M18 7v10\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-dasharray=\"2 2\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path></svg></div>\n<div class=\"orcc-badge\">Free Tool</div>\n<h3 class=\"orcc-title\">Steel Calculator for One-Way Slab</h3>\n<p class=\"orcc-desc\">Main bars and distribution bars for one-way slabs — bar count, cutting length, crank length and total steel per IS 456.</p>\n<div class=\"orcc-chips\"><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Main bars</span><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Distribution bars</span><span class=\"orcc-chip-g\">Total kg</span></div>\n<span class=\"orcc-btn\">Use Calculator<span class=\"orcc-ai\">AI</span><svg class=\"orcc-btn-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span>\n</a>\n 3. Steel — Two-Way Slab \n<a class=\"orcc-card orcc-rev orcc-d3\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/steel-calculator-for-construction/\">\n<div class=\"orcc-icon orcc-ic-purple\"><svg class=\"orcc-icon-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect height=\"20\" rx=\"2\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" width=\"20\" x=\"2\" y=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M2 8h20M2 16h20\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></path><path d=\"M8 2v20M16 2v20\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" fill=\"#d30d50\" opacity=\"0.4\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div>\n<div class=\"orcc-badge\">Free Tool</div>\n<h3 class=\"orcc-title\">Steel Calculator for Two-Way Slab</h3>\n<p class=\"orcc-desc\">Reinforcement in both directions for two-way slabs — bars along Lx and Ly, top bars, and total steel weight per IS 456:2000.</p>\n<div class=\"orcc-chips\"><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Bars along Lx</span><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Bars along Ly</span><span class=\"orcc-chip-g\">Total kg</span></div>\n<span class=\"orcc-btn\">Use Calculator<span class=\"orcc-ai\">AI</span><svg class=\"orcc-btn-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span>\n</a>\n 4. Bar Bending Schedule \n<a class=\"orcc-card orcc-rev orcc-d1\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/bar-bending-schedule-calculator/\">\n<div class=\"orcc-icon orcc-ic-purple\"><svg class=\"orcc-icon-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M3 5h18M3 5l3 3M3 5l3-3\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path><path d=\"M21 12H6M21 12l-3 3M21 12l-3-3\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path><path d=\"M3 19h18M3 19l3 3M3 19l3-3\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path></svg></div>\n<div class=\"orcc-badge\">Free Tool</div>\n<h3 class=\"orcc-title\">Bar Bending Schedule Calculator</h3>\n<p class=\"orcc-desc\">Full BBS table — bar mark, shape code, cutting length, number of bars and weight per mark. Follows SP 34 guidelines.</p>\n<div class=\"orcc-chips\"><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Cutting length</span><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Shape codes</span><span class=\"orcc-chip-g\">Weight/mark</span><span class=\"orcc-chip-g\">Full schedule</span></div>\n<span class=\"orcc-btn\">Use Calculator<span class=\"orcc-ai\">AI</span><svg class=\"orcc-btn-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span>\n</a>\n 5. Brick Calculator — amber kept \n<a class=\"orcc-card orcc-rev orcc-d2\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/brick-calculator-for-wall/\">\n<div class=\"orcc-icon orcc-ic-amber\"><svg class=\"orcc-icon-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect height=\"6\" rx=\"1.5\" stroke=\"#b45309\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" width=\"20\" x=\"2\" y=\"4\"></rect><rect height=\"6\" rx=\"1.5\" stroke=\"#b45309\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" width=\"14\" x=\"5\" y=\"14\"></rect><path d=\"M2 10h20M5 10v4M12 10v4M19 10v4\" stroke=\"#b45309\" stroke-dasharray=\"2 2\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"></path></svg></div>\n<div class=\"orcc-badge\">Free Tool</div>\n<h3 class=\"orcc-title\">Brick Calculator for Wall</h3>\n<p class=\"orcc-desc\">Brick count, mortar volume, cement bags and sand quantity for any wall size. Supports 4.5-inch and 9-inch walls with adjustable wastage.</p>\n<div class=\"orcc-chips\"><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Brick count</span><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Mortar volume</span><span class=\"orcc-chip-g\">Order qty</span><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Cement + sand</span></div>\n<span class=\"orcc-btn\">Use Calculator<svg class=\"orcc-btn-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span>\n</a>\n 6. Paint Calculator — blue kept \n<a class=\"orcc-card orcc-rev orcc-d3\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/paint-quantity-calculator/\">\n<div class=\"orcc-icon orcc-ic-blue\"><svg class=\"orcc-icon-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M18 4H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2z\" stroke=\"#1d4ed8\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path><path d=\"M8 12h8M8 8h8M8 16h4\" stroke=\"#1d4ed8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path><circle cx=\"19\" cy=\"5\" fill=\"rgba(59,130,246,0.25)\" r=\"3\" stroke=\"#1d4ed8\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></circle></svg></div>\n<div class=\"orcc-badge\">Free Tool</div>\n<h3 class=\"orcc-title\">Paint Quantity Calculator</h3>\n<p class=\"orcc-desc\">Putty, primer and finish paint quantities for any room. Enter wall dimensions, subtract doors and windows — instant coverage in litres and kg.</p>\n<div class=\"orcc-chips\"><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Putty (kg)</span><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Primer (L)</span><span class=\"orcc-chip-g\">Paint (L)</span><span class=\"orcc-chip\">Surface area</span></div>\n<span class=\"orcc-btn\">Use Calculator<svg class=\"orcc-btn-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<span id=\"res-case-studies\" style=\"display:block!important;height:0!important;\"></span>\n<div class=\"orcs-outer\">\n<div class=\"orcs-inner\">\n<div class=\"orcs-left orcs-rev-l\">\n<div class=\"orcs-summary\">\n<div class=\"orcs-sum-ey\">Case Studies</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-sum-title\">Stories from the field</div>\n<p class=\"orcs-sum-sub\">Construction companies across India and the Middle East share how SiteFlow changed daily site operations.</p>\n<div class=\"orcs-markets\">\n<div><div class=\"orcs-market-row\"><span class=\"orcs-market-name\">India</span><span class=\"orcs-market-count\">3 stories</span></div><div class=\"orcs-market-bar\"><div class=\"orcs-mb orcs-mb-50\"></div></div></div>\n<div><div class=\"orcs-market-row\"><span class=\"orcs-market-name\">Middle East</span><span class=\"orcs-market-count\">3 stories</span></div><div class=\"orcs-market-bar\"><div class=\"orcs-mb orcs-mb-50\"></div></div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-companies\">\n<div class=\"orcs-companies-lbl\">Featured companies</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-company-pills\"><span class=\"orcs-company-pill\">Reidius Infra</span><span class=\"orcs-company-pill\">SFC Infratech</span><span class=\"orcs-company-pill\">Theeran Avant</span><span class=\"orcs-company-pill\">Hydro Flow Qatar</span><span class=\"orcs-company-pill\">Cyath Contracting</span><span class=\"orcs-company-pill\">M. Munif Al Otaibi</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-sum-divider\"></div>\n<a class=\"orcs-sum-cta\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/\">View all case studies<svg class=\"orcs-cta-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-right\">\n<div class=\"orcs-head orcs-rev\">\n<div><div class=\"orcs-ey\">Client Success Stories</div><h2 class=\"orcs-h2\">Real results from <em class=\"orcs-h2-em\">real projects</em></h2></div>\n<a class=\"orcs-va\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/\">View all<svg class=\"orcs-va-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></a>\n</div>\n 1. Reidius — logo initial COLOR: rose \n<a class=\"orcs-card orcs-rev orcs-d1\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/case-study-reidius-infra/\">\n<div class=\"orcs-card-top\"><div class=\"orcs-card-person\"><div class=\"orcs-logo\" style=\"background:#fff0f3!important;\"><img alt=\"Reidius Infra\" class=\"orcs-logo-img\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\" src=\"/images/recon/website-assets-square-2025-new--1024x1024.webp\"/><span class=\"orcs-logo-initial\" style=\"display:none!important;color:#d30d50!important;\">R</span></div><div><div class=\"orcs-card-name\">Reidius Infra Pvt. Ltd.</div><div class=\"orcs-card-co\">Jaipur, India · Design and Build</div></div></div><div class=\"orcs-card-stars\"><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-outcome\">Scaled 250+ home projects from WhatsApp and Excel to a fully visible, real-time operation with zero client escalations</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-quote\">With SiteFlow, all the progress and cost details are visible in one place. Client discussions became much smoother because we are now talking with actual site data instead of guesses.</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-footer\"><div class=\"orcs-tags\"><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-g\">40% fewer client calls</span><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-p\">2 hrs saved daily</span><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-b\">30% on-time improvement</span></div><span class=\"orcs-card-link\">Read story<svg class=\"orcs-link-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span></div>\n</a>\n 2. SFC — blue initial kept \n<a class=\"orcs-card orcs-rev orcs-d2\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/sfc-infratech/\">\n<div class=\"orcs-card-top\"><div class=\"orcs-card-person\"><div class=\"orcs-logo\" style=\"background:#fff!important;\"><img alt=\"SFC Infratech\" class=\"orcs-logo-img\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\" src=\"/images/recon/GPS-based-Labour-Attendence-1.webp\"/><span class=\"orcs-logo-initial\" style=\"display:none!important;color:#1d4ed8!important;\">S</span></div><div><div class=\"orcs-card-name\">SFC Infratech Pvt. Ltd.</div><div class=\"orcs-card-co\">North India · Infrastructure and Road</div></div></div><div class=\"orcs-card-stars\"><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-outcome\">Eliminated payroll errors and gained real-time labour visibility across 50 to 100 workers on multiple concurrent sites</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-quote\">SiteFlow helped us monitor spending at activity level instead of discovering overruns later. It brought financial visibility much closer to daily execution on site, which is exactly what we needed.</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-footer\"><div class=\"orcs-tags\"><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-g\">Zero payroll errors</span><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-p\">25% labour cost reduction</span><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-b\">3 days saved monthly</span></div><span class=\"orcs-card-link\">Read story<svg class=\"orcs-link-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span></div>\n</a>\n 3. Theeran — green initial kept \n<a class=\"orcs-card orcs-rev orcs-d3\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/theeran-avant/\">\n<div class=\"orcs-card-top\"><div class=\"orcs-card-person\"><div class=\"orcs-logo\" style=\"background:#fff!important;\"><img alt=\"Theeran Avant\" class=\"orcs-logo-img\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\" src=\"/images/recon/Brand-logo-5-1.webp\"/><span class=\"orcs-logo-initial\" style=\"display:none!important;color:#059669!important;\">T</span></div><div><div class=\"orcs-card-name\">Theeran Avant</div><div class=\"orcs-card-co\">Erode, Tamil Nadu · Mechanical Works</div></div></div><div class=\"orcs-card-stars\"><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-outcome\">Replaced verbal instructions with real-time task tracking — bottlenecks visible the same day, accountability restored across all teams</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-quote\">Before SiteFlow, task assignments happened verbally or through WhatsApp messages that disappeared in conversation threads. Now every activity has a named owner and a deadline the whole team can see.</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-footer\"><div class=\"orcs-tags\"><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-g\">35% on-time improvement</span><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-p\">Same-day visibility</span><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-b\">Zero status calls needed</span></div><span class=\"orcs-card-link\">Read story<svg class=\"orcs-link-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span></div>\n</a>\n 4. Hydro Flow Qatar — COLOR: initial rose \n<a class=\"orcs-card orcs-rev orcs-d4\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/hydro-master/\">\n<div class=\"orcs-card-top\"><div class=\"orcs-card-person\"><div class=\"orcs-logo\" style=\"background:#fff!important;\"><img alt=\"Hydro Flow Qatar Pools\" class=\"orcs-logo-img\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\" src=\"/images/recon/Brand-logo-5.webp\"/><span class=\"orcs-logo-initial\" style=\"display:none!important;color:#d30d50!important;\">H</span></div><div><div class=\"orcs-card-name\">Hydro Flow Qatar Pools</div><div class=\"orcs-card-co\">Doha, Qatar · Luxury Pool Construction</div></div></div><div class=\"orcs-card-stars\"><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-outcome\">Closed the client communication gap on luxury pool projects — PDF reports from live data replacing scattered WhatsApp updates</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-quote\">We generate and share structured PDF reports directly from project data. It works reliably as a construction reporting tool without confusion between site and office numbers.</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-footer\"><div class=\"orcs-tags\"><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-g\">Instant PDF reports</span><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-p\">Client Reporting</span><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-b\">Qatar</span></div><span class=\"orcs-card-link\">Read story<svg class=\"orcs-link-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span></div>\n</a>\n 5. Cyath — amber initial kept \n<a class=\"orcs-card orcs-rev orcs-d5\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/case-study-cyath-contracting/\">\n<div class=\"orcs-card-top\"><div class=\"orcs-card-person\"><div class=\"orcs-logo\" style=\"background:#fff!important;\"><img alt=\"Cyath Contracting\" class=\"orcs-logo-img\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\" src=\"/images/recon/images.jpeg\"/><span class=\"orcs-logo-initial\" style=\"display:none!important;color:#b45309!important;\">C</span></div><div><div class=\"orcs-card-name\">Cyath Contracting LLC</div><div class=\"orcs-card-co\">Dubai, UAE · Villa and Fit-out</div></div></div><div class=\"orcs-card-stars\"><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-outcome\">Unified site operations, documentation and billing across villa and fit-out projects — one platform replacing multiple disconnected tools</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-quote\">Managing villa projects across Dubai meant juggling different tools for different tasks. SiteFlow brought everything together so nothing fell through the gaps between systems.</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-footer\"><div class=\"orcs-tags\"><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-g\">All activities consolidated</span><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-p\">Mobile access from site</span><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-b\">Dubai, UAE</span></div><span class=\"orcs-card-link\">Read story<svg class=\"orcs-link-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span></div>\n</a>\n 6. Munif — green initial kept \n<a class=\"orcs-card orcs-rev orcs-d6\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/case-study-m-munif-al-otaibi-contracting-est/\">\n<div class=\"orcs-card-top\"><div class=\"orcs-card-person\"><div class=\"orcs-logo\" style=\"background:#fff!important;\"><img alt=\"M. Munif Al Otaibi Contracting\" class=\"orcs-logo-img\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\" src=\"/images/recon/Screenshot-2024-10-28-at-12.18.36-AM.webp\"/><span class=\"orcs-logo-initial\" style=\"display:none!important;color:#059669!important;\">M</span></div><div><div class=\"orcs-card-name\">M. Munif Al Otaibi Contracting</div><div class=\"orcs-card-co\">Riyadh, Saudi Arabia · Interior Fit-out</div></div></div><div class=\"orcs-card-stars\"><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span><span class=\"orcs-cstar\">★</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-outcome\">Automated payroll and attendance on interior fit-out projects across Saudi Arabia — manual tracking errors eliminated completely</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-quote\">Tracking attendance manually across interior projects was creating constant errors and disputes. SiteFlow automated the entire process and payroll calculations now happen without anyone reconciling figures by hand.</div>\n<div class=\"orcs-card-footer\"><div class=\"orcs-tags\"><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-g\">Payroll automated</span><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-p\">Errors eliminated</span><span class=\"orcs-tag orcs-tag-b\">Real-time labour costs</span></div><span class=\"orcs-card-link\">Read story<svg class=\"orcs-link-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span></div>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<span id=\"res-comparisons\" style=\"display:block!important;height:0!important;\"></span>\n<div class=\"orcmp-outer\">\n<div class=\"orcmp-inner\">\n<div class=\"orcmp-head orcmp-rev\"><div><div class=\"orcmp-ey\">Software Comparisons</div><h2 class=\"orcmp-h2\">How SiteFlow compares to <em class=\"orcmp-h2-em\">alternatives</em></h2></div></div>\n<div class=\"orcmp-grid\">\n Card 1: Procore — SiteFlow icon rose; Procore red kept \n<a class=\"orcmp-card orcmp-card-live orcmp-rev\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/SiteFlow-vs-procore/\">\n<div class=\"orcmp-vs-row\"><div class=\"orcmp-brand\"><div class=\"orcmp-brand-ic\" style=\"background:#fff0f3!important;color:#d30d50!important;\">O</div>SiteFlow</div><span class=\"orcmp-vs-pill\">VS</span><div class=\"orcmp-brand\"><div class=\"orcmp-brand-ic\" style=\"background:#fee2e2