Modern execution vs legacy ERP</h3>\n<div class=\"orcmp-wins\"><div class=\"orcmp-win\"><div class=\"orcmp-win-dot\"><svg class=\"orcmp-win-dot-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"orcmp-win-txt\">Mobile-first — built for field adoption</span></div><div class=\"orcmp-win\"><div class=\"orcmp-win-dot\"><svg class=\"orcmp-win-dot-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"orcmp-win-txt\">No expensive implementation needed</span></div><div class=\"orcmp-win\"><div class=\"orcmp-win-dot\"><svg class=\"orcmp-win-dot-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"orcmp-win-txt\">Real-time site data, not batch reporting</span></div></div>\n<span class=\"orcmp-link\">Read comparison<svg class=\"orcmp-link-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span>\n</a>\n Card 5: Buildertrend — SiteFlow icon rose; Buildertrend red kept \n<a class=\"orcmp-card orcmp-card-live orcmp-rev orcmp-d4\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/resources/feature-comparisons/SiteFlow-vs-buildertrend/\">\n<div class=\"orcmp-vs-row\"><div class=\"orcmp-brand\"><div class=\"orcmp-brand-ic\" style=\"background:#fff0f3!important;color:#d30d50!important;\">O</div>SiteFlow</div><span class=\"orcmp-vs-pill\">VS</span><div class=\"orcmp-brand\"><div class=\"orcmp-brand-ic\" style=\"background:#fee2e2!important;color:#dc2626!important;\">B</div>Buildertrend</div></div>\n<h3 class=\"orcmp-title\">SiteFlow vs Buildertrend: Built for India vs built for the US</h3>\n<div class=\"orcmp-wins\"><div class=\"orcmp-win\"><div class=\"orcmp-win-dot\"><svg class=\"orcmp-win-dot-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"orcmp-win-txt\">India-specific compliance and workflows</span></div><div class=\"orcmp-win\"><div class=\"orcmp-win-dot\"><svg class=\"orcmp-win-dot-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"orcmp-win-txt\">INR pricing, Tally and Zoho integration</span></div><div class=\"orcmp-win\"><div class=\"orcmp-win-dot\"><svg class=\"orcmp-win-dot-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"orcmp-win-txt\">Middle East ready — Arabic project support</span></div></div>\n<span class=\"orcmp-link\">Read comparison<svg class=\"orcmp-link-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span>\n</a>\n Card 6: Powerplay — SiteFlow icon rose; Powerplay amber kept \n<a class=\"orcmp-card orcmp-card-live orcmp-rev orcmp-d5\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/resources/feature-comparisons/powerplay-vs-SiteFlow/\">\n<div class=\"orcmp-vs-row\"><div class=\"orcmp-brand\"><div class=\"orcmp-brand-ic\" style=\"background:#fff0f3!important;color:#d30d50!important;\">O</div>SiteFlow</div><span class=\"orcmp-vs-pill\">VS</span><div class=\"orcmp-brand\"><div class=\"orcmp-brand-ic\" style=\"background:#fef3c7!important;color:#b45309!important;\">P</div>Powerplay</div></div>\n<h3 class=\"orcmp-title\">SiteFlow vs Powerplay: Which is better for Indian contractors?</h3>\n<div class=\"orcmp-wins\"><div class=\"orcmp-win\"><div class=\"orcmp-win-dot\"><svg class=\"orcmp-win-dot-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"orcmp-win-txt\">Deeper subcontractor billing module</span></div><div class=\"orcmp-win\"><div class=\"orcmp-win-dot\"><svg class=\"orcmp-win-dot-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"orcmp-win-txt\">GPS attendance with payroll integration</span></div><div class=\"orcmp-win\"><div class=\"orcmp-win-dot\"><svg class=\"orcmp-win-dot-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"orcmp-win-txt\">More affordable project-based pricing</span></div></div>\n<span class=\"orcmp-link\">Read comparison<svg class=\"orcmp-link-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<span id=\"res-blog\" style=\"display:block!important;height:0!important;\"></span>\n<div class=\"orbl-outer\">\n<div class=\"orbl-inner\">\n<div class=\"orbl-head orbl-rev\">\n<div><div class=\"orbl-ey\">Construction Knowledge</div><h2 class=\"orbl-h2\">SiteFlow <em class=\"orbl-h2-em\">Blog</em></h2></div>\n<a class=\"orbl-va\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/blog/\">View all articles<svg class=\"orbl-va-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"orbl-grid\" id=\"orbl-grid\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n FAQ \n<div class=\"orfq-outer\">\n<div class=\"orfq-inner\">\n<div class=\"orfq-head orfq-rev\">\n<div class=\"orfq-eyebrow\"><div class=\"orfq-ey-dot\"></div><span class=\"orfq-ey-txt\">FAQ</span></div>\n<h2 class=\"orfq-h2\">Common questions about this page</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"orfq-grid\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/FAQPage\">\n<div class=\"orfq-item orfq-rev\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"orfq-btn\" onclick=\"orfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"orfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Are the construction calculators really free?</span><span class=\"orfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"orfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"orfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Yes, completely free with no sign-up required. All calculators on this page — steel, slab, bar bending schedule, brick, and paint — are built and maintained by SiteFlow and available to anyone in construction. There is no limit on how many times you use them.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"orfq-item orfq-rev orfq-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"orfq-btn\" onclick=\"orfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"orfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Which IS code standards do the steel calculators follow?</span><span class=\"orfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"orfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"orfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">All steel and slab calculators use IS 456:2000 formulas. Unit weight is calculated as D² divided by 163 where D is bar diameter in millimetres. The Bar Bending Schedule calculator follows SP 34 guidelines for shape codes. Lap lengths and stirrup deductions are calculated per IS standards.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"orfq-item orfq-rev\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"orfq-btn\" onclick=\"orfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"orfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Are the case study results real?</span><span class=\"orfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"orfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"orfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Yes. Every case study on this page is from an active SiteFlow client who shared their experience directly. The metrics — reduced billing errors, time saved on reporting, payroll improvements — come from the companies themselves and are documented in the full case study on each client page. No results have been estimated or extrapolated.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"orfq-item orfq-rev orfq-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"orfq-btn\" onclick=\"orfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"orfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Does SiteFlow work for companies outside India?</span><span class=\"orfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"orfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"orfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Yes. SiteFlow is actively used by construction companies in the UAE, Qatar, and Saudi Arabia. The case studies from Hydro Flow Qatar Pools in Qatar, Cyath Contracting in Dubai, and M. Munif Al Otaibi Contracting in Saudi Arabia are all live Middle East deployments. The platform supports multi-currency and works across both India and Gulf markets.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"orfq-item orfq-rev\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"orfq-btn\" onclick=\"orfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"orfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">How is SiteFlow different from Procore?</span><span class=\"orfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"orfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"orfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Procore is built for large enterprise teams with months of implementation time and USD-per-user pricing. SiteFlow is built for Indian and Middle East contractors who need BOQ-linked tracking, GPS attendance, subcontractor billing, and live P&amp;L without an implementation partner. Most SiteFlow clients are live within a week. The full breakdown is on the SiteFlow vs Procore comparison page.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"orfq-item orfq-rev orfq-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"orfq-btn\" onclick=\"orfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"orfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">How often are new blog articles published?</span><span class=\"orfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"orfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"orfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">New articles are published every week covering construction management, cost control, labour tracking, subcontractor billing, and project finance — all written specifically for Indian and Middle East contractors. The six most recent articles are shown on this page. The full archive is on the blog.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"orfq-item orfq-rev\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"orfq-btn\" onclick=\"orfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"orfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">What types of construction companies use SiteFlow?</span><span class=\"orfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"orfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"orfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">SiteFlow is used by infrastructure contractors, residential builders, interior fit-out companies, EPC firms, road contractors, and mechanical works companies. The common thread is that they manage multiple concurrent projects with active site teams and need real-time visibility without adding office staff. Company size ranges from small contractors running 5 sites to larger firms managing 50 plus projects.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"orfq-item orfq-rev orfq-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"orfq-btn\" onclick=\"orfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"orfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">How do I get started with SiteFlow?</span><span class=\"orfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"orfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"orfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Book a free 10-minute demo using the button below. The demo is a live walkthrough of the product tailored to your project type — no slides, no pitch deck. If it is a fit, onboarding is free and most teams are fully operational within a week. There is no long-term contract required to get started.</p></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n CTA \n<div class=\"orfc-outer\">\n<div class=\"orfc-inner orfq-rev orfq-d1\">\n<div class=\"orfc-eyebrow\"><div class=\"orfc-ey-dot\"></div><span class=\"orfc-ey-txt\">Try SiteFlow ERP</span></div>\n<h2 class=\"orfc-h2\">You have read enough.<br/><em class=\"orfc-h2-em\">See it on your projects.</em></h2>\n<p class=\"orfc-sub\">500 plus construction teams across India and the Middle East run their sites on SiteFlow. A 10-minute demo shows you exactly how it works for your project type.</p>\n<div class=\"orfc-btns\">\n<a class=\"orfc-btn-primary\" href=\"#ct-popup-48098\">Book a Free Demo</a>\n<a class=\"orfc-btn-outline\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/\">Read Case Studies</a>\n</div>\n<p class=\"orfc-fine\">No credit card  ·  No commitment  ·  Free onboarding</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n"
}